<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Settings</title>
    <style>
        .SettingFrame {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0 25px; /* calc(100% - 50px) 대신 padding 사용 */
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 10px;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .SettingItem {
        width: 100%;
        height: 50px;
        background: #f9f9f9;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 5px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body,
    html {
        height: 100%;
        overflow: hidden;
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }
    .Header {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 9px 24px 8px 12px;
        background: #78DDFD;
        border-bottom: 0.5px solid #E6E6E6;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .SearchInput {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        padding: 8px 16px 8px 12px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.56);
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid #E0E0E0;
    }

    .SearchForm {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 500px;
    }

    .InputField {
        flex-grow: 1;
        padding: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 4px 0 0 4px;
    }

    .SearchButton {
        background: none;
        border: none;
        padding: 0;
        cursor: pointer;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-left: none;
        border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    }

    .SearchIcon {
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
    }
    .RecentSearches {
        display: none; /* 기본적으로 숨김 */
        position: absolute;
        top: 100%; /* 부모 요소의 아래에 위치 */
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        background: #fff;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        z-index: 10;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; /* 아래 모서리를 둥글게 */
    }
    .RecentSearches h2 {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin: 10px;
    }
    .RecentSearchList {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0 10px 10px 10px;
    }
    .RecentSearchList li {
        margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .RecentSearchList a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #007bff;
    }
    .RecentSearchList a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .MainFrame {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
        height: calc(100% - 75px - 55px); /* 100% - Header height - TabBar height */
    }
    .MainFrame > div {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2px;
    }
    .MainFrame img {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 158px;
        height: auto;
        max-height: 254px;
        box-shadow: 1px 1px 7px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .MainFrame div > div {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 114px;
        height: auto;
        text-align: center;
        color: black;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 24px;
        word-wrap: break-word;
        white-space: nowrap; /* 줄바꿈 방지 */
    }

    .TabBar {
        width: 100%;
        height: 75px;
        background: white;
        box-shadow: 0 -0.5px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .Tabs {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0 7px;
    }

    .TabBarItem {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: flex-end;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2px;
        padding: 10px 27px 2px;
        opacity: 0.5;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .TabBarItem img {
        width: 23px;
        height: 23px;
    }

    .TabBarItem div {
        text-align: center;
        color: black;
        font-size: 10px;
        font-weight: 500;
    }

    .TabBarItem:first-child {
        opacity: 1;
    }

    .HomeIndicator {
        width: 134px;
        height: 5px;
        background: black;
        border-radius: 100px;
        margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .Ckt_mini{
        width: 30px;
        height: 30px;
    }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="Header">
    <div class="SearchInput">
        <form action="/search_result" method="GET" class="SearchForm">
            <input type="text" name="keyword" class="InputField" placeholder="칵테일 이름 검색">
            <button type="submit" class="SearchButton">
                <img src="/drawable/ic_search.png" alt="Search" class="SearchIcon">
            </button>
        </form>
        <div class="RecentSearches">
            <h2>Recent Searches</h2>
            <ul class="RecentSearchList">
                <li><a href="/showpost?drinkId=11000"><img class="Ckt_mini" src="/image?drinkid=11000" alt="Cocktail Image">모히또</a></li>
                <li><a href="/showpost?drinkId=11007"><img class="Ckt_mini" src="/image?drinkid=11007" alt="Cocktail Image">마가리타</a></li>
                <li><a href="/showpost?drinkId=11005"><img class="Ckt_mini" src="/image?drinkid=11005" alt="Cocktail Image">드라이 마티니</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <img class="IcProfile1" src="/drawable/ic_profile.png" width="30" height="30"/>
</div>


<div class="Content">
    <div class="ProfileImage"></div>
    <div class="SettingFrame">
        <div class="SettingItem" onclick="location.href='main2'">계정 설정</div>
        <div class="SettingItem" onclick="location.href='main2'">프로필 관리</div>
        <div class="SettingItem" onclick="location.href='main2'">공지사항</div>
        <div class="SettingItem" onclick="location.href='main2'">운영자 문의</div>
        <div class="SettingItem" onclick="location.href='main2'">어플 소개</div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="TabBar">
    <div class="Tabs">
        <div class="TabBarItem" onclick="location.href='/main2'">
            <img class="IcHome" src="/drawable/ic_home.png" />
            <div>홈</div>
        </div>
        <div class="TabBarItem" onclick="location.href='/bookmarksckt'">
            <img class="IcBookmark" src="/drawable/ic_bookmark.png" alt="My Image" />
            <div>즐겨찾기</div>
        </div>
        <div class="TabBarItem" onclick="location.href='/recipes'">
            <img class="IcCkt" src="/drawable/ic_ckt.png" />
            <div>레시피</div>
        </div>
        <div class="TabBarItem" onclick="location.href='/settings'">
            <img class="IcHome2" src="/drawable/ic_settings2.png" />
            <div>설정</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="HomeIndicator"></div>
</div>
</body>

</html>
